{"tid":1514593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國司法部擬以國安為由　反對開通連接香港光纖電纜","createTime":"2019-08-28T20:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T22:13:56.000Z","uid":41404,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2c44ccf26dd7a4a68a995eb3889da9ad612abddd","tid":1514593,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:12:51.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》報道，美國司法部可能以國家安全為理由，反對開通一條連接美國洛杉磯至香港的海底光纖電纜。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，由Google、Facebook及中國第四大電訊營運商的鵬博士電訊傳媒集團，合作鋪設這條跨太平洋的海底電纜，鋪設工程至今已完成了大半，完成後需要取得商業經營許可才能開始營運，但報道引述消息人士表示，美國司法部基於國家安全上的顧慮，當中有中國電訊傳媒集團，以及電纜在香港容易受中國控制，反對這條光纖網絡營運。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部國安事務發言人表示，外商投資或取得股權的申請個案，若果涉及國家安全和執法顧慮，美國聯邦傳播委員會會轉介司法部，司法部目前不作評論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477430-20190829.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477430-20190829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=dedafba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477430-20190829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cdb3e5bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477430-20190829.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"281623cd1199bf66108790aee6c547ed74eb35d5","tid":1514593,"uid":36915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:14:48.000Z","msg":"我大美國ho ball🇺🇸"},{"pid":"1af1d72378e3fef9f13f0edd127206847b6ace5e","tid":1514593,"uid":281328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:15:05.000Z","msg":"Good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4213de425aab11f4c7c846f07a2332054b1894c","tid":1514593,"uid":127735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:16:36.000Z","msg":"整條海底電纜托咩，講左唔用你支那貨好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f353e820b25117b8f1055e0c72dc336e6ef1ae58","tid":1